<td valign="top" class="mform" width="100%">
<p>If I remember correctly, which I am pretty sure I do, a kater is a punching dagger, so I think it should be piercing.  I can understand why its hand to hand (besides the obvious of it being monk/beastlord only), but I think piercing would be a more suitable skill. But thats just me, so, whatever...</p>
