<td valign="top" class="mform2" width="100%">
<p>Yes, a katar/qatar/khatar (the difficulties with phonetically spelling things in another language) is a punching dagger. However, qatars are usually held in a normal punching fist and then punching normally, with the blade extended through the middle knuckles, so it's reasonable to have your skill at punching be the ability rather then your skill at rapiers/normal daggers/spears. <br /> <br />-Ton</p>
